{"tid":235701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多照照鏡子，很多事情你就明白原因了。","createTime":"2017-05-09T08:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T08:18:55.000Z","uid":84102,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65fc43f8f17f35f8f93ab31d18712bcdf0c1fdbf","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"我們都知道怎麼做才是好的，問題是做不到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d7fc0ecdf754192a9cae84d20edf2bd498b444","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"明明是被社會排斥，卻做出排斥社會的樣子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f10b645369983f2878a3c80e9368c81a682e17","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"真正努力過的人，就會明白天賦的重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ef2355da9ebd3b81722e9884317d95f56384be","tid":235701,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"724371f3a0ae57b40f732184c8801c3c50c61e69","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:05:50.000Z","msg":"醜女讓人注意她的內在美。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bd6408ac3445506192c2c83559786ac5789c62","tid":235701,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醜女讓人注意她的內在美。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你很醜 但你很温柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db08bdacc3098008a8f1f9fbd7d641f1a4d1c55","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"積極生活，改變自己，其實就是裝。 <br />\n裝作自己積極樂觀，裝作自己做這些無聊的事情都感興趣，裝作自己沉穩又理性，裝作自己對所幹的事情感興趣。"},{"pid":"1e4d171197de1d9fb8d9e5687c5184582422347f","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"幸虧當局者迷，不然真的看清事實真相，很多人是承受不來的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72f448998561cc5ef72e449b55b647d6ab11795","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"有很多人對狗很好，對人卻很差。"},{"pid":"f2943551d8cc79f9d02bea6c4ee471c189fd053d","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"狗永遠是狗<br />\n人有時,不是人"},{"pid":"b2f3f05cfb6c224bd44d1a6acfb66dd87cbf66bc","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"很多時候別人對你好，並不是因為別人喜歡你，而是因為他們喜歡對人好。"},{"pid":"6f64397135570c15ae881ba4435d7d6852d972a7","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"幸福其實離我們並不遙遠，它一直在我們那些樣子好，家底好，頭腦好，積極樂觀的朋友身上。"},{"pid":"a0990602a03e2a7aa01c4fd73462db79c6d3641b","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"基因是你給的，成長環境是你給的，社會階層是你給的 <br />\n還有臉埋怨自己孩子沒出息。"},{"pid":"3bdae810913a563c8d1d21add78f35ffca0078a4","tid":235701,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDDV838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDDV838.jpg&h=6e9d2235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d9ad1541104dc11ca91b1c20918ef57d5d7a83a","tid":235701,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDDV838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDDV838.jpg&h=6e9d2235&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n898"},{"pid":"a5c3e45bfe3a13f67b28d983c7d9ebf0b414d4d7","tid":235701,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-